def fib(n):
    """
    Calculate the nth Fibonacci number.

    Args:
    n (int): The position of the Fibonacci number.

    Returns:
    int: The nth Fibonacci number.
    """
    if n < 1:
        return n
    return fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)
